      <title>FEMA removed dozens of Camp Mystic buildings from 100-year flood map before expansion, records show</title>
      <author>The Associated Press</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/12/nx-s1-5465564/fema-removed-camp-mystic</link>
