      <title>In Myanmar, a rush for rare earth metals is causing a regional environmental disaster</title>
      <author>Michael Sullivan</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/12/nx-s1-5437955/myanmar-rare-earth-metals-regional-environmental-disaster</link>
