      <title>'Helping every dang soul': Beloved camp director was among those lost in Texas flooding</title>
      <author>Frank Morris</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/12/g-s1-77295/texas-flooding-kerrville-victim-heart-o-the-hills-camp-mystic-jane-ragsdale</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/07/12/g-s1-77295/texas-flooding-kerrville-victim-heart-o-the-hills-camp-mystic-jane-ragsdale</comments>
