      <title>Federal judge orders stop to indiscriminate immigration raids in Los Angeles</title>
      <author>Adrian Florido</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/11/nx-s1-5462618/federal-judge-orders-stop-to-indiscriminate-immigration-raids-in-los-angeles</link>
